text: Tamworth Football Club is an English association football club based in Tamworth, Staffordshire. The club participates in the Northern Premier League under the management of Andy Peeks The club was formed in 1933. ==Other websites== * *Heritage site *Fan's Forum Category:1930s establishments in England Category:1933 establishments in the United Kingdom Category:English football clubs Category:Organisations based in Staffordshire
